                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-355-off1922 t18300415-355-crimeloc1925"></join>. On the 12th of April, about five o'clock in the afternoon, the prisoner came into the shop and stood by the side of another customer; she asked for nothing, but the roll of silk was lying on the counter - she had a linen cloth in her hand, she laid it on the silk, and took it out; I followed her just outside the door - I took her with it; she confessed it directly - this is it; it has the private mark on it.</p>
